hadiths[30]{hadithnumber,text}:
1371,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qiyame-Ramazan ki targheeb diya kartey they baghair uskey ke aap waajibi taur par unko hukm den. phir farmatey they : '' jisney emaan ki bina par aur taqarrub aur sawab ki gharz se Ramazan ka qiyam kiya, uskey picchley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki rihlat (wafat) ho gaee aur mamla aisey hi raha . uskey baad khilaafate Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke ibtidaai (shuruati) daur mein bhi yehi soorat rahi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Aqeel , Yunus aur Abu-Uwais ne aisey hi riwayat kiya hai : ''yani jisney Ramazan ka qiyam kiya.'' aur Aqeel ki riwayat hai : ''jisney Ramazan ke rozey rakhey aur uska qiyam kiya.''"
1372,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfooan bayan kartey hain : ''jisney emaan aur taqarrub aur sawab ki niyat se Ramazan ke rozey rakhey , uskey pichley gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain. aur jisney emaan aur taqarrub aur sawab ke liye lailatul-qadr ka qiyam kiya, uskey pichley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Abi Kaseer aur Muhammad bin Amr ne Abu-Salma se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai."
1373,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki biwi se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein Namaz padhi (yani Ramazan ki raat mein qiyam farmaya ( to logon ne bhi aap ke sath Namaz padhi . aapney agli raat phir Namaz padhi to log bhi bahut ho gaey . phir jab wo teesri raat jama huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar se nikley hi nahin. jab subh hui to farmaya : ''tum ne jo kiya wo maine dekha hai aur mujhey tumhari taraf nikalney se bas yehi (rukawat) rahi ke mujhey andesha hua kahin ye Namaz tum par farz na kar di jaey.'' aur ye Ramazan ki baat hai.
1374,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke log masjid mein tukdiyon mein bat kar Namaz padhtey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya to maine aap ke liye chatai bichha di. aapney Namaz padhi . ... . aur ye qissa bayan kiya. ... . aur aapney farmaya : ''logo ! maine Allah ke fazal se raat ghaflat mein nahin guzari aur na tumhara yahan jama hona mujh par makhfi (chhipa hua) raha hai.''
1375,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Ramazan ke rozey rakhey , aapney hamarey sath koi qiyam na kiya, yahan tak ke mahiney main eik hafta baqi reh gaya , to aapney hamein qiyam karwaya , yahan tak ke tihai raat ho gaee . jab ( aakhir sey) chhatti raat aai to aapney qiyam na karaya . jab paanchwin aai to hamein qiyam karwaya , yahan tak ke aadhi raat guzar gaee . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kash aap hamein baqiya raat bhi uska qiyam karwa detey ? to aapney farmaya : '' insan jab Imam ke sath Namaz padhta hai aur uskey farigh honey tak uskey sath rehta hai to uskey liye puri raat ka qiyam shumar kiya jata hai.'' jab chauthi raat aai to aapney qiyam na karaya . jab teesri raat aai to aapney apney aqaarib , biwiyon aur doosrey logon ko jama farmaya aur hamein qiyam karaya , yahan tak ke hamein fikr hui ke kahin hamari ''falah'' (kaamyabi) hi na reh jaey. (Jubair ne kaha ( maine puchha ke ''falah'' se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha ''sehr''. phir baqiya raaton mein aapney ham ko qiyam nahin karaya."
1376,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab Ramazan ka ( aakhiri ( hissey shuru hota, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raaton ko jaagtey , apni kamar kas letey aur apney ghar walon ko bhi jagaatey. Imam Abu-Dawud bayan kartey hain ke Abu yaafur ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Ubaid bin Niastaas hai."
1377,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur dekha ke log Ramazan mein masjid ki eik janib mein Namaz padh rahey hain. aapney puchha : ''unko kya hai?'' kaha gaya ke un logon ko Quran yaad nahin hai aur Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padh rahey hain to ye log bhi unke sath Namaz padh rahey hain, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhoney durust kiya aur bahut khoob kiya.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye hadees qawi nahin hai. Muslim bin Khalid Zaeef hai."
1378,"Zirr-bin-Hajeesh kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aey Abul Munzir ! mujhey lailatul-qadr ke baarey mein bataaiye kyonkey hamarey sahab ( Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se uskey baarey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : jo shakhs sara saal qiyam karta rahey, wo usey pa lega . to unhoney kaha : Allah Abu-Abdur-Rehman (yani ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) par rehem farmaai , Allah ki qasam ! unhen khoob maloom hai ke ye Ramazan mein hoti hai. (Musaddad ne izafa kiya) lekin unhoney na pasand kiya ke log ( sirf Ramazan hi par) takiya kar lein ya unhoney chaha hai ke log usi par takiya na kar lein. ( phir Sulaiman aur Musaddad dono ne kaha : ( qasam Allah ki ! ye Ramazan ki sattaaisween shab ko hoti hai, In-sha-Allah na kaha : maine kaha : aey Abul Munzir ! aap ko uska kaisey ilm hua ? unhoney kaha : us alamat sey, jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein batai hai. ( Aasim ne kaha ( maine Janab Zirr se puchha : wo alamat kya hai? unhoney kaha : us raat ki subah ko Suraj tasht (thaal/ tanbey ki badi plate ( ki tarah nikalta hai aur ooncha honey tak us mein shuaa (kiran) (aur hiddat (garmi) ( nahin hoti."
1379,"Zamra bin Abdullah bin Unais apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke main bani Salma ki eik majlis mein tha aur main un sab se chhota tha, unhoney kaha : kaun hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hamarey liye lailatul-qadr ke mutalliq poochh aaye ? aur ye Ramazan ki ikkeeswin taareekh ki subah thi. isliye main nikla aur maghrib ki Namaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath padhi . phir main aap ke ghar ke darwazey par khada ho gaya. aap merey paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''andar aa jao.'' main andar chala gaya , aap ko ashaaiya pesh kiya gaya. mujhey yaad hai ke main khana kam honey ki wajeh se jhijhak raha tha (yani bahut kam kha raha tha.) jab farigh ho gaey to farmaya : ''mujhey merey jootey do.''  chunanche aap khadey ho gaey aur main bhi aap ke sath uth khada hua . aapney farmaya : ''shayad tum kisi kaam se aaye they?'' maine arz kiya : haan ! bani Salma ki eik jamaat ne mujhey aap ki khidmat mein bheja hai, wo log lailatul-qadr ke mutalliq daryaft karna chahtey hain. aapney farmaya : ''aaj kaun si raat hai? maine kaha : aaj baaisween hai. aapney farmaya : ''yehi raat hai.'' phir aapney apni baat dohraee aur farmaya : ''agli raat hai.'' yani teisween raat ."
1380,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main dehat mein rehta hun aur bi-hamd-illaah wahin Namaz padhta hun. to aap mujhey kisi raat (lailatul-qadr) ke mutalliq irshad farma den ke us raat mein yahan is masjid mein aa jaun . aapney farmaya : '' teisween ki raat ko aa jana .) Muhammad bin Ibrahim ne kaha : ( maine unke bete ( Zamra bin Abdullah ( se kaha : to tumharey walid kaisey kya kartey they? unhoney kaha : wo Asr padh kar masjid mein dakhil ho jaya kartey they aur kisi hajat ke liye bahir na nikaltey they, yahan tak ke subh ki Namaz padhtey . isliye Namaz subah ke baad apni sawari masjid ke darwazey par paatey they, us par baithtey aur apni manzil par) dehat mein) chaley aatey."
1381,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''lailatul-qadr ko Ramazan ki aakhiri das ( raaton ( mein talash karo . aakhiri naween , saatween aur paanchween raat mein.''"
1382,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ke darmiyani ashrey mein aetikaf kiya kartey they. aapney eik saal aetikaf kiya, yahan tak ke jab ikkeesween raat aa gaee aur (qabl azeen) aap us raat ko apney aetikaf se nikal aaya kartey they, to aapney farmaya : '' jisney merey sath aetikaf kiya hai to wo aakhiri hisse mein aetikaf karey. maine us raat (lailatul-qadr) ko dekha hai, magar bhulwaa diya gaya hun. aur maine apney aap ko dekha hai ke uski subah ko pani aur mitti (keechad) mein sajda kar raha hun. chunanche tum usey aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo aur usey her taaq raat mein talash karo.'' Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : chunanche usi raat barish ho gaee aur masjid ki chhat , jo chhadiyon ki bani hui (chhappar numaa) thi , tapak padi. meri aakhon ne dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki peshani aur naak par pani aur mitti (keechad) ka nishan tha aur ye ikkeeswin raat ki subah thi."
1383,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo . naween , saatween aur paanchween raat mein talash karo.'' (yani aakhir mahine se.) maine kaha : aey Abu-Saeed ! aap ginti ham se behtar jantey hain. unhoney kaha : haan . maine kaha : naween , saatween aur paanchween se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : jab ikkeesween guzar jaey to uskey baad wali naween hai aur jab teisween guzar jaey to uskey baad wali saatween hai aur jab pachchisween guzar jaey to uskey baad wali paanchween hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : mujhey nahin maloom ke is hadees mein mujh par koi baat chhupi rahi hai ya nahin. (kyonkey hatmi (pakki/mukammal) taareekh ke ta'yun mein shubha sa rehta hai.)"
1384,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : ''usey (yani lailatul-qadr ko ( Ramazan ki satrahwin , ikkeeswin aur teiswin raat mein talash karo.'' phir khamosh hi rahey ."
1385,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri saat raaton mein shabbe-qadr talash karo.''
1386,Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' sattaaisween ki raat shabbe-qadr hai.''
1387,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se lailatul-qadr ke baarey mein puchha gaya jabkey main sun raha tha, aapney farmaya : ''ye sarey Ramazan mein hoti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : usko Sufiyan aur Shoba ne Abu-Is'haq sey, ibne-Umar se mauqufan riwayat kiya hai aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak marfoo bayan nahin kiya hai."
1388,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya tha : '' Quran karim ko eik mahiney mein khatam kiya karo.'' unhoney kaha : mujhey is-se ziyada ki taqat hai. aapney farmaya : '' bees dino mein khatam kiya karo.'' kaha : mujhey is-se ziyada ki taqat hai. farmaya : ''pandarah dino mein khatam kiya karo.'' unhoney kaha : main is-se bhi ziyada ki taqat paata hun. aapney farmaya : ''das dino mein khatam kiya karo.'' kaha : mujhey is-se bhi ziyada ki himmat hai. farmaya : ''saat din mein khatam kiya karo aur is se kam hergiz na karna . Imam Abu-Dawud ne farmaya ke Muslim bin Ibrahim ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai.
1389,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''har mahiney teen din rozey rakho aur eik mahiney mein Quran padho .''aap mujh se kami karwaatey rahey aur main kami karta raha . bil-aakhir aapney farmaya : '' eik din roza rakho aur eik din iftaar karo.'' Ata kehtey hain ke maine aur merey sathiyon ne merey walid ( saahib ( se riwayat kerney mein ikhtilaf kiya. ham mein se kuch saat din riwayat kartey hain aur kuch paanch (yani qirate-Quran mein).
1390,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main kitney dino mein Quran padhun ? aapney farmaya : ''eik mahiney mein.'' unhoney kaha : main is-se ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun. Abu-Musa ( ibne Musanna ( ne ye jumla baar baar dohraayaa . yani unhoney is muddat mein kami chahi. bil-aakhir aapney farmaya : ''saat dino mein padho.'' unhoney kaha : main is-se bhi ziyada taqat rakhta hun. aapney farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne teen din se kam mein Quran padha , usney isey samjha hi nahin.''"
1391,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : '' Quran eik mahiney mein padha karo.'' unhoney kaha : mujh mein (us se ziyada ki) taqat hai. aapney farmaya : ''isey teen roz mein mukammal padha karo.'' Abu-Ali ( raawi Sunan Abi Dawood ( kehtey hain : maine Imam Abu-Dawud ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal kaha kartey they ke Esa bin Shaazaan daanaa aadmi hai.
1392,ibne Hadi kehtey hain ke Janab Naafe bin Jubair bin Mut-im (Taabai) ne mujh se puchha ke tum kitney dino mein Quran padhtey ho? maine kaha ke main iskey ( lazimi ( hissey nahin karta hun ( balke jo taufiq hoti hai padh leta hun. (us par Janab Naafe ne kaha ke is tarah mat kaho ke main iskey hissey nahin karta kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''maine Quran ka eik Juz (hissa) padha .'' (ibn Hadi ne) kaha : mera khayal hai ke shaikh ne usko Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai.
1393,"Hazrat Aus bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham saqeef ke wafad ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. (is wafad mein sey) haleef (kuchh) log Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ke mehman ban gaey aur) doosrey ( bani Malik ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney eik khemey mein iqaamat di. Musaddad ne kaha ke Aus bin Huzefa is wafad mein shamil they jo saqeef ki taraf se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha. Aus bin Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Isha ke baad hamarey yahan rozaana tashrif latey aur baat cheet kartey they. Abu-Saeed ne kaha : aap apney paon par khadey khadey baaten kartey aur ziyada der khadey rehney ki wajeh se kabhi eik paon par zor de-kar khadey hotey kabhi doosrey par . aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aam taur se apni qaum Quraish ke sath beete halaat bayan farmaya kartey. farmatey : ''ham barabar na they, balke kamzor aur naatawaan (kamzor) they. ... . Musaddad ke alfaz hain : ''makkey mein. ... jab ham Madiney aagey to ham mein aur un mein ladaai shuru ho gaee . kabhi ham un par ghalib aatey kabhi wo.'' eik raat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney muqarrara waqt par aaney mein takheer kar di to ham ne kaha aaj raat aap takheer se tashrif laye hain? farmaya : '' mera eik Juz (hissa) Quran ka rehta tha, maine uski tilawat mukammal kiye baghair aana pasand na kiya.'' Aus kehtey hain : maine as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maloom kiya ke aap log Quran ke hissey kis tarah kartey hain? to unhoney kaha ke pehla hissey teen soorton ka , (Baqara , Aale-Imran aur Nisaa) doosra hissey paanch soorton ka (Maayda se Tauba tak) teesra hissey saat soorton ka (Yunus se Nahal tak) chautha hissey nau soorton ka (bani Israel se Furqaan tak) , paanchwan hissey giyara soorton ka (Shoo'araa' se Yaaseen tak) chhata hissey tehra soorton ka (Saffat se Hujuraat tak) aur saatwan hissey mufassal (tafseel) ka (Qaaf se aakhir tak). Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Abu-Saeed ki hadees ziyada kamil hai."
1394,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne teen din se kam mein Quran padha usney isey samjha hi nahin.''
1395,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke kitney dino mein Quran padha jaey ? aapney farmaya : ''chaalis dino mein.'' phir farmaya : ''eik mahiney mein.'' phir kaha : ''bees dino mein'' phir kaha : ''pandarah dino mein.'' phir kaha : ''das dino mein.'' phir kaha : ''saat dino mein.'' aur saat se kam nahin kiya.
1396,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga ke main eik rakat mein pura Juz mufassal (aakhiri manzil) padh leta hun. unhoney kaha : kya tum she'ron ki tarah jaldi jaldi padhtey ho? ya sukhi raddi khajuron ki tarah bikherte ho? halanke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) barabar qism ki do-do suraten eik rakat mein padha kartey they. ''(النجم)'' aur ''(الرحمن)'' eik rakat mein. ''(اقتربت)'' aur ''(الحاقة)'' eik rakat mein.''(الطور)'' aur  ''(الذاريات)'' eik rakat mein. ''(إذا وقعت)'' aur ''(ن)'' eik rakat mein. ''(سأل سائل)'' aur ''(النازعات)'' eik rakat mein. ''(ويل للمطففين)'' aur ''(عبس)'' eik rakat mein. ''(المدثر)'' aur ''(المزمل)'' eik rakat mein. ''(هل أتى )'' aur ''(لا أقسم بيوم القيامة)'' eik rakat mein. ''(عم يتساءلون)'' aur ''(المرسلات)'' eik rakat mein. ''(الدخان)'' aur ''(إذا الشمس كورت)'' eik rakat mein. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke soorton ki ye mazkura tarteeb Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki taaleef (sankalan) hai. (yani unke musahaf (kitab) ki tarteeb is tarah thi. )
1397,"Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha jabkey wo Baitullah ka tawaf kar rahey they, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ko sura baqara ki aakhiri do aayaten padh ley , ye usko kafi ho jati hain.''"
1398,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne das aayaton se qiyam kiya wo ghaafilon mein shumar nahin hota. aur jo sau aayaton se qiyam karey wo ''قانتين'' (Aabedeen) mein likha jata hai. aur jo hazar aayaton se qiyam karey wo ''المقنطرين'' (be inteha sawab jama kerney walon) mein likha jata hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ibne Hujaira Al Asghar se murad Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin Hujaira hai.
1399,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey kuch Quran padhaaiye . aapney farmaya : '' teen suraten padho jin ki ibtida (shuruat) mein ''الرا'' hai.''(Yunus, Hood aur yousuf) usney kaha : meri umr badi ho gaee hai. dil sakht ho gaya hai (bhool jata hun) aur zaban moti ho gaee hai (is wajeh se ye badi badi suraten yaad nahin kar sakta). aapney farmaya : ''to ''Ha-Mim'' wali teen suraten padh lo.'' is par bhi usney apni pehli baat hi kahi. aapney farmaya : '' to Musabbihaat wali teen suraten yaad kar lo.'' (jinkey shuru mein (سبح) ya (يسبح) aata hai.) is par bhi usney apni wohi baat dohrani aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi Jaame surat padha dijiye. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko sura (إذا زلزلت الأرض) padhaai, aakhir tak. tab wo shakhs kehney laga : qasam us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq ke sath bheja hai ! main is se kabhi ziyada na karunga. phir wo peeth pher kar chala gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do martaba farmaya : ''is chhotey se mard ne najat pai.''"
1400,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''Quran karim ki eik surat tees aayaton wali, apney padhney waley ke liye sifarish karegi, yahan tak ke usey bakhsh diya jaeyga.'' (murad hai) (تباركَ الذِي بيدِهِ المُلكُ)."
